{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","National Minimum Wage rates"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/national-minimum-wage-rates.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/national-minimum-wage-rates"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"1859","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"The National Minimum Wage rates valid from 1 October 2012","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:13:31+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>The National Minimum Wage rate per hour depends on your age and whether you\u2019re an apprentice.</p>\n</div>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Year</th>\n      <th>21 and over</th>\n      <th>18 to 20</th>\n      <th>under 18</th>\n      <th>Apprentice</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><strong>2012 (current rate)</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>\u00a36.19</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>\u00a34.98</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>\u00a33.68</strong></td>\n      <td><strong>\u00a32.65</strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2011</td>\n      <td>\u00a36.08</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.98</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.68</td>\n      <td>\u00a32.60</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2010</td>\n      <td>\u00a35.93</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.92</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.64</td>\n      <td>\u00a32.50</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The age groups were different before 2010. There were no National Minimum Wage rates for apprentices.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Year</th>\n      <th>22 and over</th>\n      <th>18 to 21</th>\n      <th>under 18</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2009</td>\n      <td>\u00a35.80</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.83</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.57</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2008</td>\n      <td>\u00a35.73</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.77</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.53</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2007</td>\n      <td>\u00a35.52</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.60</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.40</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2006</td>\n      <td>\u00a35.35</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.45</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.30</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>2005</td>\n      <td>\u00a35.05</td>\n      <td>\u00a34.25</td>\n      <td>\u00a33.00</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Read the information on <a href=\"/your-right-to-minimum-wage/who-gets-the-minimum-wage?\" title=\"who is entitled to the minimum wage\">who is entitled to the minimum wage</a> or use the <a href=\"National-Minimum-Wage-calculator\" title=\"National Minimum Wage Calculator\">National Minimum Wage calculator</a> to check whether the National Minimum Wage is being paid.</p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Your pay, tax and the national minimum wage","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/working%2Ftax-minimum-wage.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes national minimum wage rates, keeping pay records and pay rights","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=working%2Ftax-minimum-wage","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working/tax-minimum-wage"},"parent":{"title":"Working, jobs and pensions","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/working.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes holidays and finding a job","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=working","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Your right to the minimum wage","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/your-right-to-minimum-wage.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/your-right-to-minimum-wage","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"171","business_proposition":false}}]]],"parts":null}